pageContext.claim: “Look what I've done. Look what I've done. Israel was -- we're signing deals all over the place. These guys that are lecturing all the time, they don't have a clue. They're clueless. They were clueless. That's why for 40 years you got nothing except blood in the sand.”
pageContext.analysis: Most of Trump's deals are relatively minor updates of previous trade deals negotiated by previous presidents. Upon becoming president, he tanked the Trans Pacific Partnership, major trade deal in Asia negotiated by Obama.
